 <li><a href="/car/carma/new_rp">Set your privacy preferences</a> to help us align our infrastructure's behavior with your expectations.</li>
 <li><a href="/car/carma/selfservice/sites">Review sites and services</a> who have asked for your personal information.</li>
 <li>Check this site from time to time for updates and tips on protecting your privacy in other ways!</li>
